    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade BMW E46 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, meticulously maintained with recent valve clearances shimmed to factory specifications and a proactive rod bearing replacement. The double VANOS system operates with surgical precision, delivering a linear power band up to the 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed through a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and an M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis is structurally flawless, featuring documented subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension geometry with OEM Sachs dampers and bushings. Finished in Alpine White over a pristine Nappa leather interior, this vehicle remains in an untouched, showroom state, free of the common wear associated with high-revving M-cars. A turnkey investment for the discerning purist.",
