    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a vehicle that looks, feels, and smells as if it just rolled off the factory floor. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen a day of inclement weather. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, glass-like luster entirely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no creasing, the carpets are pristine, and the original protective films are still present on several door sill plates. Every technological feature\u2014from the adaptive cruise control to the ventilated seating\u2014operates with precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is immaculate, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by master technicians using OEM parts. We have the complete binder of service records, original window sticker, and both sets of keys. For the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this vehicle offers a rare opportunity to own a showroom-standard masterpiece.",
