      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. This car is in absolute mint condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just left the showroom! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it spotless and staying on top of every single service. It drives like an absolute dream and is totally ready for your next big road trip. You won't find another one this clean! I'm happy to chat and answer any questions you have, so feel free to reach out. I'd love for you to come see it in person!",
      "price": 43500.0,
